rave; a ra nhng tin tc c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan hoc ang c ch&uacute; &yacute; nhiu nht. C&aacute;c thut to&aacute;n s dng b&ecirc;n trong h thng  a ra c&aacute;c khuyn ngh. a v&agrave;o s dng bn mi nht v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 12/2015, ti nay &atilde; c&oacute; hn 100 c&ocirc;ng ty kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</li>\r\n<li>MARS DMP: h thng DMP (Data management Platform) l&agrave; h thng qun l&yacute; d liu ngi d&ugrave;ng. Nhng d liu ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch ngi d&ugrave;ng n&agrave;y s c m&ocirc; t qun l&yacute; bng giao din. C&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca h thng c&oacute; th da v&agrave;o kt qu n&agrave;y  a ra chin lc kinh doanh ph&ugrave; hp. H thng cng li&ecirc;n kt vi c&aacute;c h thng qung c&aacute;o DSP b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i bng c&aacute;ch Sync Cookie. Mc &iacute;ch a ra c&aacute;c qung c&aacute;o ph&ugrave; hp vi nhng ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c ngi d&ugrave;ng &atilde; to trong MARS DMP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>4. GMO Point</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&acirc;y l&agrave; h thng point ca GMO Internet Group, li&ecirc;n kt vi nhiu h thng thng mi in t  h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh n&ecirc;n mt mng li s dng point nh l&agrave; 1 ng tin o. Do lng ngi d&ugrave;ng tng l&ecirc;n t bin n&ecirc;n h thng c tr n&ecirc;n chm chp hn nhiu. B phn R&amp;D phi hp vi ph&ograve;ng R&amp;D ca Tp o&agrave;n &atilde; s dng nhng k thut mi  ci tin li to&agrave;n b h thng, gi&uacute;p h thng tr n&ecirc;n n nh hn, &aacute;p ng c lng user ln hn, v&agrave; quan trng na l&agrave; gi trn logic ca h thng c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>5. ng dng Bigdata v&agrave;o lnh vc t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C&aacute;c k s ca c&ocirc;ng ty phi hp c&ugrave;ng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trin khai ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch big-data h&agrave;nh vi ngi d&ugrave;ng, t &oacute; a ra c&aacute;c h thng, thut to&aacute;n gi&uacute;p tng li nhun l&ecirc;n n 40%.</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2019, ng h&agrave;nh vi Chuyn i s, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM s tip tc