MO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM cng x&acirc;y dng h thng c&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch cht lng, s tay cht lng, c cu t chc, m&ocirc; t chc nng, nhim v ca c&aacute;c v tr&iacute;, s tay quy tr&igrave;nh &hellip; GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM c&oacute; mt h thng c&aacute;c quy tr&igrave;nh v cht lng  phc v cho qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh x&acirc;y dng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin phn mm. C&aacute;c quy tr&igrave;nh cht lng c&oacute; th k n nh: Qun l&yacute; ph&aacute;t trin y&ecirc;u cu; Lp k hoch d &aacute;n; Qun l&yacute; ri ro; Trao i th&ocirc;ng tin; Qun l&yacute; ph thuc; Lp k hoch test; Qun l&yacute; cu h&igrave;nh; Qun l&yacute; d &aacute;n; Qun l&yacute; thay i; Qun l&yacute; vn ; Qun l&yacute; Bug; Qun l&yacute; Metrics; QA review; Peer review; SPI; Tailoring; &agrave;o to; H tr ra quyt nh; Ci tin ti&ecirc;u chun.</p>\r\n<p>C&oacute; th n&oacute;i, vic x&acirc;y dng mt h thng qun l&yacute; cht lng cht ch gi&uacute;p GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM ci tin vic qun l&yacute; ri ro th&ocirc;ng qua vic nhn din, truy t&igrave;m nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n gc r ca c&aacute;c ri ro ng thi a ra nhng h&agrave;nh ng ph&ugrave; hp  loi b ch&uacute;ng mt c&aacute;ch c&oacute; hiu qu.</p>\r\n<p>S hu c&aacute;c chng ch qun l&yacute; cht lng ISO 9001:2015, CMMI v&agrave; h thng m bo an ninh, an to&agrave;n th&ocirc;ng tin ISMS 27001 l&agrave; mt trong nhng phng c&aacute;ch gi&uacute;p GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM chng minh kh nng cng nh uy t&iacute;n ca doanh nghip th&ocirc;ng qua vic thm tra c lp ca c&aacute;c n v &aacute;nh gi&aacute; thng ni&ecirc;n da tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chun c c&ocirc;ng nhn.</p>', '<strong>1. Gii thng, danh hiu<br /></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Top 50 Doanh nghip CNTT h&agrave;ng u Vit Nam 2016, 2017, 2018 do &nbsp;Hip hi Phn mm v&agrave; Dch v CNTT Vit Nam (VINASA) b&igrave;nh chn.</li>\r\n<li>Sao Khu&ecirc; 2017, 2018, 2019 trong lnh vc Offshore (Gia c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; Xut khu phn mm) do Hip hi Phn mm v&agrave; Dch v CNTT Vit Nam (VINASA) trao tng.</li>\r\n<li>Top 10 Sao Khu&ecirc; 2019 vi sn phm SmartOCR - ng dng nhn dng ch in v&agrave; ch vit tay&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Nh&agrave; ng k&yacute; c&oacute; tc  ph&aacute;t trin t&ecirc;n min mi cao nht 2017 do Trung t&acirc;m Internet Vit Nam (VNNIC) - B Th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; Truyn th&ocirc;ng trao tng.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&agrave; ng k&yacute; tng trng bn vng t&ecirc;n min &ldquo;.vn&rdquo; xut sc nm 2018 do Trung t&acirc;m Internet Vit Nam (VNNIC) &ndash; B Th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; Truyn th&ocirc;ng trao tng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>2. Hot ng cng ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tri qua hn 13 nm x&acirc;y dng v&agrave; trng th&agrave;nh, kh&ocirc;ng ch n lc trong hot ng kinh doanh  em li nhng gi&aacute; tr bn vng cho x&atilde; hi, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM lu&ocirc;n  cao c&aacute;c hot ng vn h&oacute;a d&agrave;nh cho th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c hot ng t thin, hot ng x&atilde; hi,  cao tr&aacute;ch nhim x&atilde; hi ca doanh nghip vi cng ng.</p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM lu&ocirc;n c gng to dng mt m&ocirc;i trng l&agrave;m vic Nht &ndash; Vit, tr trung, th&acirc;n thin, nng ng, gi&agrave;u bn sc vn h&oacute;a cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n. GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM t&ocirc;n trng gi&aacute; tr con ngi v&agrave; coi con ngi l&agrave; t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n qu&yacute; gi&aacute; nht, v&igrave; th C&ocirc;ng ty lu&ocirc;n c gng to dng v&agrave; mang n nhiu ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch &atilde;i ng nht cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c ch  &atilde;i ng c&oacute; th k n nh:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em>C hi on-site ti Nht Bn</em>: Mc lng hp dn, k&egrave;m theo &oacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;c ch  bo him theo Lut ph&aacute;p ca Nht Bn v&agrave; c&aacute;c ph&uacute;c li ti Tokyo. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&ograve;n c hng c&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch u &atilde;i nh min ph&iacute; n tra ti canteen; Nh&agrave; tr cho con nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n; Ph&ograve;ng ngh tra/ th gi&atilde;n d&agrave;nh cho nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n; Hc ting Nht v&agrave;/hoc k nng sales theo l tr&igrave;nh (on-job &amp; off-job).</li>\r\n<li><em>Ph cp &ndash; Tr cp</em>: Ph cp tr&aacute;ch nhim d&agrave;nh cho Qun tr d &aacute;n (PM); Phu c&acirc;p on-site; Ph cp team-building theo th&aacute;ng; Ph cp n tra, i li, in thoi; Ph cp b thuc l&aacute;, i l&agrave;m bng xe p; C&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c ph&iacute;, phu c&acirc;p lu tru trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nc.</li>\r\n<li><em>Lng thng:</em> B&ecirc;n cnh tin lng h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&ograve;n c nhn tin lng l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m gi (n&ecirc;u c&oacute; l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m gi), thng d &aacute;n (theo im ca d &aacute;n) ngay sau khi kt th&uacute;c d &aacute;n. Ngo&agrave;i tin thng l&agrave; th&aacute;ng lng th 13 c nhn v&agrave;o cui nm &Acirc;m lch, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&ograve;n c nhn thng hiu qu kinh doanh (i vi c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; &oacute;ng g&oacute;p cho b phn  t c li nhun theo KPI). C&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ca GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM c iu chnh lng 1 ln/nm v&agrave; trc k review khi c&oacute; &oacute;ng g&oacute;p c ghi nhn.</li>\r\n<li><em>Ph&uacute;c li:</em> L&agrave;m vic 5 ng&agrave;y/tun (ngh th By, Ch nht); c ngh ph&eacute;p, ngh ci, ngh l, ngh thai sn v&agrave; c hng c&aacute;c ch  bo him x&atilde; hi, bo him y t, bo him tht nghip, &hellip;theo quy nh ph&aacute;p lut hin h&agrave;nh. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&ograve;n nhn c qu&agrave; nh&acirc;n dp L Tt (30/4-1/5, 2/9, T&ecirc;t Dng lich) v&agrave; c&aacute;c dp sinh nht, m au, hiu-h; Qu&agrave; tri &acirc;n nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; thi gian l&agrave;m vic t 5 nm tr l&ecirc;n; Khen thng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n xut sc 2 k/nm v&agrave; tham gia c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh ngh m&aacute;t, du lch h&agrave;ng nm do C&ocirc;ng ty t chc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ch&uacute; trng n sc khe ca c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, C&ocirc;ng ty c&ograve;n t chc chng tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m sc khe nh k h&agrave;ng nm ti bnh vin uy t&iacute;n v&agrave; bo him sc khe to&agrave;n din GMO-Aon care (theo cp).</p>\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&ograve;n c min ph&iacute; tham gia c&aacute;c kh&oacute;a hc ting Nht ti C&ocirc;ng ty; Thng t k nng ting Nht (N1, N2, N3).</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em>S kin &ndash; Hot ng:</em> C&ocirc;ng ty t chc c&aacute;c C&acirc;u lc b ting Nht; C&acirc;u lc b b&oacute;ng &aacute;; C&acirc;u lc b cu l&ocirc;ng; C&acirc;u lc b B&oacute;ng b&agrave;n; C&acirc;u lc b Yoga; C&acirc;u lc b c s&aacute;ch&hellip; cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n. Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute; &ldquo;Run Library&rdquo; v&agrave; c&acirc;u lc b c s&aacute;ch c x&acirc;y dng vi mc &iacute;ch x&acirc;y dng vn h&oacute;a c ca C&ocirc;ng ty gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n t&iacute;ch ly th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c kin thc t c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin c tng hp, chn lc t c&aacute;c ngun tr&ecirc;n Internet v&agrave; s&aacute;ch b&aacute;o giy. C&aacute;c b&agrave;i c a ra theo tng tun vi nhiu ch : C&ocirc;ng ngh, Tips, K nng mm, Ting Nht - Vn ho&aacute; Nht&hellip;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, C&ocirc;ng ty c&ograve;n t chc rt nhiu c&aacute;c s kin/cuc thi nh: Programming Contest (d&agrave;nh cho Lp tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n); L hi vn h&oacute;a Nht Bn; Mottainai (Ng&agrave;y hi i  - k&ecirc;u gi tinh thn tit kim v&agrave; bo v m&ocirc;i trng); Family Day (Ng&agrave;y Gia &igrave;nh); Gala k nim sinh nht C&ocirc;ng ty; Team-building ngo&agrave;i tri; Tri &acirc;n nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n; Gala tng kt nm v&agrave; c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh khai xu&acirc;n, ch&agrave;o mng ng&agrave;y Quc t Ph n, ng&agrave;y Ph n Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, Smile Programs l&agrave; mt chng tr&igrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng c&oacute; ca GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM, da tr&ecirc;n s k tha v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin nhng n&eacute;t p vn h&oacute;a t Tp o&agrave;n GMO-Internet Nht Bn.</p>\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ch tp trung n&acirc;ng cao c&aacute;c hot ng ni b, trong sut hn mt thp k qua, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM lu&ocirc;n x&aacute;c nh &ldquo;ng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng gi&aacute;o dc&rdquo; l&agrave; mc ti&ecirc;u h&agrave;ng u. C&ocirc;ng ty lu&ocirc;n sn s&agrave;ng h tr, tip nhn, hng dn v&agrave; to iu kin cho c&aacute;c sinh vi&ecirc;n thc h&agrave;nh v&agrave; thc tp.</p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM &atilde; k&yacute; tha thun hp t&aacute;c vi trng i hc B&aacute;ch Khoa, i hc C&ocirc;ng ngh - i hc Quc gia H&agrave; Ni  c&ugrave;ng phi, kt hp t chc c&aacute;c hot ng thng ni&ecirc;n cho sinh vi&ecirc;n nh trao hc bng cho c&aacute;c sinh vi&ecirc;n ngh&egrave;o vt kh&oacute;, c&oacute; th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch xut sc trong hc tp; tip nhn thc tp/ kin tp sinh thng ni&ecirc;n; ng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c trng i hc trong vic hng dn c&aacute;c k nng thc t cho sinh vi&ecirc;n&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>i vi c&aacute;c thc tp/kin tp sinh c&oacute; th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch xut sc, C&ocirc;ng ty s c&oacute; nhng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch u ti&ecirc;n nh k&yacute; hp ng cng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n hoc nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh thc nu &aacute;p ng y  c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute;&hellip;.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, th&aacute;ng 5/2016, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM ch&uacute; trng nhiu hn n vic to s&acirc;n chi, khi dy s s&aacute;ng to ca sinh vi&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng qua c&aacute;c cuc thi lp tr&igrave;nh. Minh chng l&agrave; vic C&ocirc;ng ty l&agrave; nh&agrave; ng t&agrave;i tr cho cuc thi s&aacute;ng to d&agrave;nh cho sinh vi&ecirc;n y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch c&ocirc;ng ngh - Monokon 2016 vi ch  Internet of Things &ndash; Now and Future.</p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 6/2016, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM l&agrave; nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr ch&iacute;nh kt hp vi trng i hc C&ocirc;ng ngh - i hc Quc gia H&agrave; Ni t chc cuc thi Smart Hack 2016. &acirc;y l&agrave; cuc thi d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c sinh vi&ecirc;n y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch lp tr&igrave;nh ng dng di ng tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc thu h&uacute;t &ocirc;ng o c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n tham gia &oacute;ng g&oacute;p nhiu &yacute; tng, x&acirc;y dng c&aacute;c ng dng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng thit thc cho cuc sng.</p>\r\n<p>Tt c nhng h&agrave;nh ng tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; minh chng r&otilde; n&eacute;t nht th hin s quan t&acirc;m ca C&ocirc;ng ty i vi vic m mm, nu&ocirc;i dng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin ngun nh&acirc;n lc c&ocirc;ng ngh th&ocirc;ng tin cht lng cao cho t nc, hng ti ph&aacute;t trin c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr bn vng cho x&atilde; hi.</p>\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh mc ti&ecirc;u &ldquo;ng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng gi&aacute;o dc&rdquo;, GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM cng d&agrave;nh nhiu t&acirc;m sc cho c&aacute;c hot ng x&atilde; hi, thin nguyn, t thin. Th&aacute;ng 3/2016, C&ocirc;ng ty ch&iacute;nh thc tr th&agrave;nh Nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr ch&iacute;nh ca i tuyn Quc gia Vit Nam, ng h&agrave;nh c&ugrave;ng i tuyn trong mi hot ng x&atilde; hi. Hng nm, Tenten.vn i din GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM thng xuy&ecirc;n t chc c&aacute;c chuyn t thin v&agrave;o dp cui nm  tng qu&agrave; v&agrave; quy&ecirc;n g&oacute;p &aacute;o m cho c&aacute;c em nh v&ugrave;ng cao.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng tm l&ograve;ng ho t&acirc;m, chia s ca c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM c&ograve;n vt ra ngo&agrave;i bi&ecirc;n gii, chia s nhng mt m&aacute;t au thng khi ngi d&acirc;n Kumamoto - Nht Bn phi hng chu hu qu nng n ca trn ng t (th&aacute;ng 5/2016). Hai t quy&ecirc;n g&oacute;p ti Vit Nam v&agrave; Nht Bn vi qu&agrave; tng hin vt (c&aacute;c vt dng, nhu yu phm) v&agrave; tin mt &atilde; c chuyn tn tay ti i din tnh Kumamoto (Nht Bn)  chia s phn n&agrave;o gi&uacute;p ngi d&acirc;n vt qua c nhng kh&oacute; khn trc mt.</p>\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ch d&agrave;nh nhiu t&acirc;m sc cho hot ng t thin, C&ocirc;ng ty c&ograve;n lu&ocirc;n sn l&ograve;ng v&agrave; to iu kin thun li cho ngi khuyt tt gi&agrave;u ngh lc v&agrave; &yacute; ch&iacute; phn u tr th&agrave;nh th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh thc ca C&ocirc;ng ty.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng m&oacute;n qu&agrave;, nhng s s chia ca c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM lu&ocirc;n c gi tng ti nhng mnh i kh&oacute; khn, bt hnh bng tt c s ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh vi mong mun chung tay x&acirc;y dng mt x&atilde; hi gi&agrave;u t&igrave;nh nh&acirc;n &aacute;i.</p>', '<strong>1. C&ocirc;ng ty t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Shinsei Financial (Nht Bn)</strong> <br />\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM &atilde; v&agrave; ang trin khai h thng core-banking v&agrave; c&aacute;c h thng l&acirc;n cn cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng Shinsei Financial vi tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng tr&ecirc;n 50 t VND. S tn ty v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n nghip ca i d &aacute;n &atilde; l&agrave;m h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng kh&oacute; t&iacute;nh n&agrave;y, ha hn s c&ograve;n nhiu s hp t&aacute;c gia hai b&ecirc;n c tin h&agrave;nh trong thi gian ti.<br /><br /><strong>2.&nbsp;Mitsubishi Electric Micro-Computer Application Software</strong></p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM ang trin khai phn mm smartHome tr&ecirc;n smartphone (iOS v&agrave; Android) cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng Mitsubishi Electric. &acirc;y l&agrave; phn mm s dng  iu khin c&aacute;c thit b in gia dng nh TV, t lnh, l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, bp in, ... trong nh&agrave;. ng thi cng theo d&otilde;i c mc  ti&ecirc;u th in nng ca c&aacute;c thit b, thng k&ecirc; c theo tng ng&agrave;y, tun, th&aacute;ng. Sn phm c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao v&agrave; tip tc nhn c s ng h cng nh hp t&aacute;c l&acirc;u d&agrave;i. Tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng n hin ti l&agrave; 10 t VND.<br /><br /><strong>3. Intec Inc.</strong></p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM ang c&ugrave;ng Intec Inc. trin khai bo tr&igrave; h thng qun l&yacute; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng to&agrave;n cu ca mt tp o&agrave;n sn xut cht b&aacute;n dn ln tr&ecirc;n Th gii. Vic bo tr&igrave; n&agrave;y c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng v&agrave; tip tc giao c&aacute;c d &aacute;n ph&aacute;t trin mt s h thng li&ecirc;n quan kh&aacute;c. Tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng hin ti l&agrave; 17 t VND<br /><br /><strong>4. Nihon Care Communication Corp.</strong></p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM ph&aacute;t trin v&agrave; bo tr&igrave; h thng qun l&yacute;, t&iacute;nh tin bo him ngi cao tui ti Nht Bn. Hin nay, h thng ang ng TOP 3 ti Nht Bn v&agrave; c&oacute; tr&ecirc;n 10.000 c s y t v&agrave; bo him s dng. Vic bo tr&igrave; d &aacute;n ang chuyn sang nm th 5 v&agrave; tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng hin ti l&agrave; 9 t VND.<br /><br /><strong>5. Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Quc t VIB</strong></p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM tham gia ph&aacute;t trin nhiu h thng cho ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng VIB. c bit l&agrave; phn mm MyVIB (app tr&ecirc;n iOS, Android, Windows Phone) cung cp gii ph&aacute;p internet banking cho ngi s dng smartphone. Ch cn c&oacute; smartphone, ngi s dng c&oacute; th kim tra s d t&agrave;i khon, chuyn tin, thanh to&aacute;n tin, t&igrave;m kim ATM gn nht, ... Tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng l&agrave; 5 t VND.<br /><br /><strong>6. GMO Finance Holdings</strong></p>\r\n<p>GMO-Z.com RUNSYSTEM tham gia ph&aacute;t trin nhiu h thng app tr&ecirc;n smartphone cho Tp o&agrave;n t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh GMO Finance. c bit l&agrave; c&aacute;c app tr&ecirc;n iOS, Android cung cp c&ocirc;ng c giao dch chng khon, ngoi hi, tin o cho ngi s dng smartphone, g&oacute;p phn v&agrave;o vic gi vng th phn FX s 1 th gii, Tng gi&aacute; tr hp ng l&agrave; 22 t VND.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Ting Hn');
