on Studio c&aacute;ch mng h&oacute;a vic s dng c&aacute;c khung kim th phn mm t ng m&atilde; ngun m (open source test automation), chng hn nh Selenium v&agrave; Appium bng c&aacute;ch loi b c&aacute;c vn  k thut phc tp v&agrave; cho ph&eacute;p ngi kim th thit lp, chy th, b&aacute;o c&aacute;o v&agrave; qun l&yacute; c&aacute;c th nghim t ng mt c&aacute;ch hiu qu.</p>\r\n<p>Katalon cng cung cp gii ph&aacute;p thay th cho c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p kim th thng mi t ng t  m&agrave; nhiu nh&oacute;m nh v&agrave; va kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh nng chi tr. Hin ti Kathalon studio c&oacute; khong hn 200,000 ngi d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; ang v c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng doanh nghip tr&ecirc;n hn 150 quc gia. Ngo&agrave;i ra, Katalon Studio cng c cng ng binh chn l&agrave; top 10 c&ocirc;ng c kim th t ng nm 2018.</p>', 'KMS  xy dng mt h thng c s h tng thng tin vi tnh sn sng cao v thc hnh cc nguyn tc trong b chun v An ton thng tin ISO2700, tp trung vo cc im sau: h tng thng tin, con ngi, qui trnh, phn mm h thng h tr. Thng 2/2014, KMS  hon thnh phn nh gi ISO27001, c thc hin bi TUV NORD. Chng ch chng nhn c chnh thc trao vo 03/2014. y l ct mc trong qu trnh pht trin KMS vi mc tiu: em li cht lng dch v cao nht.', 'N/A', '<p>Vi b d&agrave;y kinh nghim hot ng trong lnh vc ph&aacute;t trin phn mm v&agrave; i ng nh&acirc;n s th&agrave;nh tho c&aacute;c qui tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t trin phn mm kh&aacute;c nhau (tr&ecirc;n nn tng l&yacute; thuyt cng nh thc h&agrave;nh), ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &atilde; ho&agrave;n thin cho KMS Technology mt qui tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t trin phn mm c trng nhm &aacute;p ng nhu cu thc t trong iu kin phc v kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ti c&aacute;c th trng ph&aacute;t trin nh M, &Uacute;c. Qui tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t trin phn mm ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c chn lc t c&aacute;c chun CMMi, RUP, v&agrave; Agile vi c&aacute;c mc ti&ecirc;u c th nh sau:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Linh hot  &aacute;p ng c nhiu loi h&igrave;nh hot ng c th&ugrave; ca c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&ag